[32m│[0m `decoy.txt` if it exists, otherwise it reads from `flag.txt`. Since the      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m current flag shows "this is just the decoy", the real flag is likely in      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `flag.txt`.                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
